Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.47,1:41:56.55,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}去那個唯一惦念的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.91,1:42:01.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}從未放棄
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.95,1:42:10.65,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}緊緊相握 手心的溫度
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.12,1:42:23.07,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}很抱歉讓你落淚
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.31,1:42:29.27,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}就如突然到來的明信片
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.76,1:42:36.99,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}各種悲傷湧上心頭
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.36,1:42:42.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}在行進的途中
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.30,1:42:56.11,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}我會帶著微笑 隻身奔向你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.33,1:43:05.64,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}奔向你 只想見你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.17,1:43:10.48,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}向著沒有傷痛的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.59,1:43:14.64,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}一直都被照耀著
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.52,1:43:23.01,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}你回望我的 那份目光
