Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.55,1:21:11.60,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}たとえ異国の白い街でも
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.72,1:21:18.04,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}風がのどかなとなり町でも
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.34,1:21:23.97,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}私はたぶん同じ旅人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.20,1:21:27.23,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}遠いイマージュ
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.38,1:21:31.00,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}水面におとす
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.37,1:21:33.71,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}時は川
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.80,1:21:36.90,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}きのうは岸辺
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.26,1:21:42.79,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}人はみなゴンドラに乗り
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.89,1:21:48.72,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}いつか離れて
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.17,1:21:55.00,Song_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}想い出に手をふるの
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.97,1:40:43.85,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}思い出してごらんよ
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.10,1:40:50.37,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}幼い日　胸を震わせた
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.75,1:40:57.58,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}言葉にできないまま
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.08,1:41:03.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}残してきたものを
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.48,1:41:09.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}青空にそこだけ
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.73,1:41:15.65,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}影落とし　山にかかる雲
